ri i livet kommer til \u00e5 klare det. Jeg har ikke gitt opp, sier Thea Heirsaunet."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "sport"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "05149ad97ddf9263e9c69dff8cd0c28996bd127f1308e73eb7d3c7d2080b9582"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-02-09T16:27:30.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Syv operasjoner - fortsatt daglige smerter."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article2118969.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/montasje"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/73e10342469c2de16882a63d2ebea77d3819e50b.jpg?595a2881"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["H\u00e5ndballmarerittet -adressa.no", "Nyoperert \u2013 igjen", "Utviklet allergi", "Klandrer ikke legene", "Ikke feilbehandling", "Merket ikke meniskskade", "Andre kan l\u00e6re", "Skal tilbake"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "73e10342469c2de16882a63d2ebea77d3819e50b"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "sport"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "health-and-fitness"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["smerter", "operasjon", "smertene", "skade", "legene"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["olavs hospital", "st. olavs hospital", "adresseavisen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "levanger"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["jon olav drogset", "thea heirsaunet"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "sport"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article2118969.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/montasje"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value"